{"tid":702392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"西鐵吉車班次 有又煩 無又煩揮手區","createTime":"2018-06-15T00:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T01:03:57.000Z","uid":156628,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"12f1a891817d394ce0dab5284f4430b1a54c0bca","tid":702392,"uid":156628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:44:54.000Z","msg":"天水圍站有兩班特別班次<br />\n08:07am <br />\n08:18am <br />\n吉車出發<br />\n知道的人 會企白箭嘴排隊<br />\n未等倒吉車 <br />\n會打側身等其他人係中間上車<br />\n等吉車埋站 <br />\n至會企係綠色箭嘴上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日就有位阿叔 <br />\n吉車埋緊站都唔行去綠色箭嘴中間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 四條隊變5條隊<br />\n有人叫番佢排去中間<br />\n阿叔：「咩中間?講野一舊一舊」<br />\n排緊4條隊變5條<br />\n原先有得坐 都變無得坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己坐倒就得 其他人坐唔坐倒都無所謂<br />\n影左佢相<br />\n如果想排特別班次都坐倒<br />\n就唔好排佢隔籬啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/084301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F084301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=adf492e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd0c2b8e5d7e867fedd32e97d04e985c111befca","tid":702392,"uid":156628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天水圍站有兩班特別班次<br />\n08:07am <br />\n08:18am <br />\n吉車出發<br />\n知道的人 會企白箭嘴排隊<br />\n未等倒吉車 <br />\n會打側身等其他人係中間上車<br />\n等吉車埋站 <br />\n至會企係綠色箭嘴上<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日就有位阿叔 <br />\n吉車埋緊站都唔行去綠色箭嘴中間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 四條隊變5條隊<br />\n有人叫番佢排去中間<br />\n阿叔：「咩中間?講野一舊一舊」<br />\n排緊4條隊變5條<br />\n原先有得坐 都變無得坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己坐倒就得 其他人坐唔坐倒都無所謂<br />\n影左佢相<br />\n如果想排特別班次都坐倒<br />\n就唔好排佢隔籬啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/084301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F084301_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=adf492e9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> up錯圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/085359_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F085359_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e173f28d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"563ef5d4aaba4620bd0d3cd02fc08bd304bbce30","tid":702392,"uid":23433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T00:57:52.000Z","msg":"屌你當呢度facebook?"},{"pid":"307943bd664da47c523e6a3786d7b70301ffc43e","tid":702392,"uid":156628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T01:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你當呢度facebook?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明"}]}